## Update

**Description:** Update device to the database

**Address:** localhost:port/device/update

**Request Type:** POST

**API Parameters:**

|No|Name|Data Type|IsRequired|Sample|Description|Note|
|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|
|1|id|Integer|Yes|2|Device id||
|2|maker|String|Yes|newMaker|Device Maker||
|3|model|String|Yes|Model7|Device model||
|4|measurement|String|Yes|temperature|Measurement type of the device||
|5|measurement_unit|String|Yes|Â°C|Unit of the measurement||
|6|status|String|Yes|idle|Device status(using, idle, matenance)||



**Result:**

Data Type: Text

|No|Name|Data Type|IsRequired|Sample|Description|Note|
|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|
|1|body|String|Yes|Update success|Result of response||



**Result Sample:**
```
Update success
```